quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  33,21,"In God´s messenger you have a fine model for someone who looks forward to [meeting] God and the Last Day, and mentions God frequently"
  33,22,"When believers saw the Coalition, they said: ´This is what God and His messenger have promised us. God and His messenger have told the truth.\" It merely increased them in faith and submission"
  33,23,"Some believers are men who are sincere in what they pledge to God, while others have already fulfilled their mortal duty, and still others are waiting [their chance]; they have not changed in the least"
  33,24,"so God may reward the truthful for their truthfulness and punish hypocrites if He so wishes, or else relent towards them. God is Forgiving, Merciful"
  33,25,"God sent the ones who disbelieved back in their fury; they did not accomplish any good. God spares believers the trouble of fighting; God is Strong, Powerful"
  33,26,"He has tossed some People of the Book who had backed them up, out of their strongholds and cast panic into their hearts; one group you killed while you captured another group"
  33,27,"He let you inherit their land, their homes and their property, plus a land you have not yet set foot on. God is Capable of everything"